instruction: Create a list of 10 items that every kitchen needs.
output:
Every kitchen needs:
- Pots and pans
- Knives and cutting boards
- Appliances (blender, toaster, microwave)
- Utensils (spatula, ladle, measuring cups)
- Storage containers 
- Stovetop accessories (pans, trivets)
- Dinnerware (plates, bowls, cups)
- Tea towels
- Cooking oils and herbs
- Cleaning supplies (dish soap, sponge, dish cloths)
